text: thumb Jean-Michel Couve (born January 3, 1940 in Le Muy, Var) is a member of the National Assembly of France. He represents the Var department, and is a member of the Union for a Popular Movement. ==References== Category:1940 births Category:Living people Category:People from Var (department) Category:Rally for the Republic politicians Category:Union for a Popular Movement politicians Category:Deputies of the 12th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 13th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 14th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic
title: Jean-Michel Couve
